---
sliders: [
  {
    copy: 'Photo by Nugroho Wahyu from Pexels',
    link: 'https://www.pexels.com/photo/brown-wooden-table-with-chair-3097112/',
    src: 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/3097112/pexels-photo-3097112.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1920',
    title: 'Sunlight Interior'
  },
  {
    copy: 'Photo by Max Vakhtbovych from Pexels',
    link: 'https://www.pexels.com/photo/contemporary-apartment-with-cozy-sofa-and-minimalist-furniture-6585764/',
    src: 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/6585764/pexels-photo-6585764.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1920',
    title: 'Living Room'
  },
  {
    copy: 'Photo by Dayvison de Oliveira Silva from Pexels',
    link: 'https://www.pexels.com/photo/cozy-living-room-design-with-comfy-sofa-and-creative-lamp-5696287/',
    src: 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/5696287/pexels-photo-5696287.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1920',
    title: 'Bedroom'
  }
]
---

<header class="uk-position-relative uk-light" tabindex="-1" uk-slideshow="animation: fade; autoplay: true; ratio: false; pause-on-hover: false" uk-scrollspy="cls: uk-animation-fade; repeat: true">
  <ul class="uk-slideshow-items uk-height-viewport">
    {% for slide in sliders %}
      <li>
        <img src="{{ slide.src }}" alt="{{ slide.copy }}" uk-cover="" />
        <div class="uk-position-center-right uk-position-large uk-text-right">
          <h1 class="uk-heading-medium uk-margin-small">
            {{ slide.title }}
          </h1>
          <blockquote class="uk-margin-small">
            <footer>
              <a class="uk-link-muted" href="{{ slide.link }}" target="_blank">
                {{ slide.copy }}
              </a>
            </footer>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
  <div class="uk-position-top-left uk-position-large">
    <a class="uk-icon-button uk-margin-small-right" uk-icon="facebook" href="#"></a>
    <a class="uk-icon-button uk-margin-small-right" uk-icon="instagram" href="#"></a>
    <a class="uk-icon-button uk-margin-small-right" uk-icon="pinterest" href="#"></a>
    <a class="uk-icon-button uk-margin-small-right" uk-icon="twitter" href="#"></a>
    <a class="uk-icon-button uk-margin-small-right" uk-icon="youtube" href="#"></a>
  </div>
  <nav class="uk-position-bottom-right uk-position-large uk-text-right">
    <a class="uk-button uk-button-default uk-button-large uk-margin-small-left uk-text-nowrap" href="#about">
      About
    </a>
    <a class="uk-button uk-button-secondary uk-button-large uk-margin-small-left uk-text-nowrap" href="#our-work">
      Our Works
    </a>
    <a class="uk-button uk-button-default uk-button-large uk-margin-small-left uk-text-nowrap" href="#contact">
      Contact
    </a>
  </nav>
</header>

<div class="uk-grid-match uk-grid-collapse" uk-grid="" uk-scrollspy="target: > div; cls: uk-animation-fade; repeat: true">
  <div class="uk-width-5-6 uk-width-3-4@s uk-width-1-2@l" id="about">
    <div class="uk-padding-small uk-margin-auto-vertical">
      <div class="uk-flex uk-flex-wrap uk-flex-bottom">
        <h2 class="uk-heading-medium">
          About
        </h2>
        <blockquote>
          <footer>
            <a class="uk-link-muted" href="https://www.pexels.com/photo/crates-mounted-on-wall-1090638/" target="_blank">
              Photo by Lisa from Pexels
            </a>
          </footer>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      <p class="uk-text-large">
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Consequuntur, repellat mollitia blanditiis nobis ratione rerum culpa nihil enim!
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="uk-width-1-6 uk-width-1-4@s uk-width-1-2@l uk-cover-container uk-height-viewport">
    <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1090638/pexels-photo-1090638.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1280" alt="Photo by Lisa from Pexels" uk-cover="" />
  </div>

  {% for item in ourWorks.slice(0,2) %}
    <div class="uk-width-1-2" id="{{ 'our-work' if loop.first }}">
      <div class="uk-cover-container uk-height-viewport uk-light">
        <img src="{{ item.image.src }}" alt="{{ item.image.copy }}" uk-cover="" />
        <div class="uk-position-center uk-position-small uk-text-center">
          <h2 class="uk-heading-medium">
            {{ 'Our' if loop.first else 'Works' }}
          </h2>
          {% if loop.first %}
            <a class="uk-button uk-button-secondary uk-button-large uk-margin-small-left" href="our-work/{{ item.path }}.html">
              See
            </a>
          {% else %}
            <a class="uk-button uk-button-secondary uk-button-large uk-margin-small-left" href="our-work.html">
              All
            </a>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        <div class="uk-position-bottom-right uk-position-small">
          <blockquote>
            <footer>
              <a class="uk-link-muted" href="{{ item.image.link }}" target="_blank">
                {{ item.image.copy }}
              </a>
            </footer>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  {% endfor %}

  <div class="uk-width-1-6 uk-width-1-4@s uk-width-1-2@l uk-cover-container uk-height-viewport">
    <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3205568/pexels-photo-3205568.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1280" alt="Photo by cottonbro from Pexels" uk-cover="" />
  </div>
  <div class="uk-width-5-6 uk-width-3-4@s uk-width-1-2@l" id="contact">
    <div class="uk-padding-small uk-margin-auto-vertical">
      <div class="uk-flex uk-flex-wrap uk-flex-bottom">
        <h2 class="uk-heading-medium">
          Contact
        </h2>
        <blockquote>
          <footer>
            <a class="uk-link-muted" href="https://www.pexels.com/photo/women-and-men-standing-near-table-3205568/" target="_blank">
              Photo by cottonbro from Pexels
            </a>
          </footer>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      <form>
        <label class="uk-display-block uk-margin">
          <span class="uk-h3 uk-margin-small uk-display-block">
            Your e-mail
          </span>
          <input class="uk-input uk-form-large" placeholder="example@mail.com" type="email" />
        </label>
        <label class="uk-display-block uk-margin">
          <span class="uk-h3 uk-margin-small uk-display-block">
            Your name
          </span>
          <input class="uk-input uk-form-large" placeholder="Tanya" type="text" />
        </label>
        <label class="uk-display-block uk-margin">
          <span class="uk-h3 uk-margin-small uk-display-block">
            Your message
          </span>
          <textarea class="uk-textarea uk-form-large uk-resize-vertical" placeholder="I have a small house. How you can help?" rows="5"></textarea>
        </label>
        <button class="uk-button uk-button-secondary uk-button-large">
          Send
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>